	<TextInfo>
		<Text Type="Business Summary" lastModified="2015-02-03T22:17:46">F&amp;C Capital and Income Investment Trust PLC is a United Kingdom-based investment company. The Companys investment objective is to secure long-term capital and income growth from a portfolio consisting mainly of FTSE All-Share companies. The Companys major investments are in financials, oil and gas, consumer good, utilities, telecommunications, healthcare, consumer services, industrials, basic materials and technology sectors. The Company is managed by F&amp;C Management Limited, which is a wholly owned subsidiary of F&amp;C Asset Management plc.</Text>
		<Text Type="Financial Summary" lastModified="2016-02-19T14:02:45">BRIEF: For the fiscal year ended 30 September 2015, F&amp;C Capital &amp; Income Investment Trust revenues decreased 7% to L10.2M. Net income decreased 10% to L8M. Revenues reflect Gain/Loss Investment decrease from L125K to -L586K, Bond interest decrease from L331K to L0K, Derivative income decrease from L274K to L0K. Net income also reflects Other expenses increase of 11% to L588K (expense). Dividend per share remained flat at L0.10.</Text>
